snippet.title: TT Isle of Man 2 | Gameplay Video #1
snippet.description:
Pre-order the game at your local Retail Store and get the Ducati 900 as a bonus! 

TT Isle of Man – Ride on the Edge 2 will features classic bikes such as the MV Agusta 500 Three, Norton NRS 588, Suzuki XR69, Yamaha TZ 750 and the Ducati 900, a legendary bike ridden by Mike Hailwood®. 

#TTIsleofMan2 will be available in March 2020 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, PC and later on Nintendo Switch.
